---
title: Double Prawn Wontons & Umami Veggie Soup with Egg Noodles & Sesame Seeds
description: Plump prawn wontons and silky egg noodles swimming in a fragrant veggie-packed broth—this soul-warming soup is a slurp-worthy delight. Sprinkle over a good pinch of sesame seeds for that perfect crunch, and dig right in!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67c0f6b060686822766eb414-4c1fe662.jpeg
